c SPDX-License-Identifier: PMPL-1.0-or-later
c 3-colouring of a triangle (K_3): vertices v1,v2,v3, colours r,g,b
c Variables 1..9 indexed as (v-1)*3+c for v∈{1,2,3}, c∈{1=r,2=g,3=b}
c Each vertex gets at least one colour:
c   v1: 1∨2∨3,  v2: 4∨5∨6,  v3: 7∨8∨9
c Each vertex has at most one colour (3 × 3 pairwise):
c Adjacent vertices don't share colour (3 edges × 3 colours):
c Expected: SATISFIABLE (any proper 3-colouring)
p cnf 9 21
1 2 3 0
4 5 6 0
7 8 9 0
-1 -2 0
-1 -3 0
-2 -3 0
-4 -5 0
-4 -6 0
-5 -6 0
-7 -8 0
-7 -9 0
-8 -9 0
-1 -4 0
-2 -5 0
-3 -6 0
-1 -7 0
-2 -8 0
-3 -9 0
-4 -7 0
-5 -8 0
-6 -9 0
